        The Body Corporate Records Search in Queensland: What Unit Sellers Need to Order
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Every buyer's solicitor orders a body corporate records search on a Queensland unit. Here is what is in it, what a clean result looks like, and why sellers should read it before buyers do.
      </p>
